{"tid":474654,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[玩命] 試食淘寶非油炸薯片","createTime":"2017-11-20T11:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T00:54:04.000Z","uid":79353,"like":5,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"da1243c8cee4a89767649565eb5a33c65d4fd209","tid":474654,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T11:17:21.000Z","msg":"話說最近無聊想試下大陸零食玩下命<br />\n所以上淘寶求其揀左一箱自稱非油炸薯片<br />\n叫做 阿婆家的。<br />\n<br />\n我買package有九隻味混合埋一細箱, 其中有三隻味係重覆<br />\n<br />\n開箱想食辣就開孜然味食下啦。<br />\n一撕開就聞到好勁孜然味, 好似行過譚記聞到就知係孜然雞翼咁<br />\n<br />\n講下口感先<br />\n咬落真係好脆, 有冇油炸過就唔知了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然一包得好少, 但每一塊都夠晒脆<br />\n<br />\n講下味道<br />\n食孜然先係因為嗜辣<br />\n不過食落唔覺得特別辣<br />\nD味粉落得唔平均, 開頭食幾塊覺得冇乜特別孜然味道<br />\n<br />\n最尾食晒成條膠兜, 口腔裡有好輕微孜然辣味的餘韻<br />\n不過對本愛辣人妖黎講, 完全唔夠辣囉。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n孜然味總結: <br />\n口感佳, 味道每塊不均, 整體辣味不足<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/191637_aa80faa94bceddd277f390f17fdad993.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F191637_aa80faa94bceddd277f390f17fdad993.jpg&h=edcfd336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/191638_1b36387d16dda78e9fa61e8b1ababf56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F191638_1b36387d16dda78e9fa61e8b1ababf56.jpg&h=caba6db0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6230b051fb3d5743f9edb6960d7a911520833bd","tid":474654,"uid":5834,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T11:28:28.000Z","msg":"咁柒個樣都俾得落錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721ed017bba26df58b1afbab57e4a35123e0a8db","tid":474654,"uid":35508,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T11:30:07.000Z","msg":"買lays青瓜同檸檬味好過啦"},{"pid":"ec8f588a934e559786be78