/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511f92df410a0095ff68f72bff2150e5cdf8029b","tid":474654,"uid":34863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:31:27.000Z","msg":"好撚平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買都買啲咁柒嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4452e587f65ac54681968c185540944e1b0710db","tid":474654,"uid":31921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T12:33:18.000Z","msg":"譚仔係無孜然雞翼的 仲有請你去買枝孜然粉lam真啲辣唔辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8a30714002be81a6d33698ed75d185e6ed5345","tid":474654,"uid":7306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T14:58:35.000Z","msg":"強國垃圾都要17個幾包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9ba8434f7cc8ddd759335c1e0369b4addbdd9c","tid":474654,"uid":65603,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T18:17:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>譚仔係無孜然雞翼的 仲有請你去買枝孜然粉lam真啲辣唔辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n土匪雞翼上面嗰啲係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95f5976b39e96d85afaabb10afbc04492a94508","tid":474654,"uid":81178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T00:54:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>譚仔係無孜然雞翼的 仲有請你去買枝孜然粉lam真啲辣唔辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n土匪雞翼上面嗰啲係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n土匪"}]}